# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Disbursement — Cash Out ke Rekening Bank
#
# Prasyarat:
#   - Merchant harus punya saldo (lihat 04_mutation.http)
#   - Merchant status active
#   - Rekening bank sudah ditambah via POST /v1/merchants/me/bank-accounts
#   - Admin sudah verifikasi rekening via PATCH /admin/merchants/:id/bank-accounts/:aid/verify
#   - Provider yang support: xendit, doku (bukan midtrans/ipaymu)
#
# PENTING: Disbursement pakai bank_account_id (UUID) dari rekening yang sudah
# terdaftar dan terverifikasi, BUKAN input bank_code + account_number langsung.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@baseUrl        = http://localhost:8080
@apiKey         = wpay_test_GANTI_DENGAN_API_KEY_DARI_RESPONSE
@disbursementId = GANTI_DENGAN_DISBURSEMENT_ID
# Isi dengan id rekening bank dari GET /v1/merchants/me/bank-accounts
@bankAccountId  = GANTI_DENGAN_BANK_ACCOUNT_ID


### 1. Disbursement via Xendit
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: disb-xendit-001

{
  "provider": "xendit",
  "bank_account_id": "{{bankAccountId}}",
  "amount": 500000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "description": "Pencairan saldo mingguan"
}


### 2. Disbursement via DOKU
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Idempotency-Key: disb-doku-001

{
  "provider": "doku",
  "bank_account_id": "{{bankAccountId}}",
  "amount": 250000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "description": "Refund order #98765"
}


### 3. List semua disbursement (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements?page=1&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### 4. Get detail disbursement
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements/{{disbursementId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### ERROR CASES ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Provider tidak support disbursement → 400 Bad Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "provider": "midtrans",
  "bank_account_id": "{{bankAccountId}}",
  "amount": 100000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "description": "Test — should fail"
}


### Rekening belum diverifikasi admin → 422 Unprocessable Entity
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "provider": "xendit",
  "bank_account_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "amount": 100000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "description": "Test — rekening tidak valid"
}


### Saldo tidak cukup → 402 Payment Required
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "provider": "xendit",
  "bank_account_id": "{{bankAccountId}}",
  "amount": 999999999999,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "description": "Test — saldo tidak cukup"
}


### bank_account_id tidak valid UUID → 400 Bad Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/disbursements
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "provider": "xendit",
  "bank_account_id": "bukan-uuid",
  "amount": 100000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "description": "Test — bank_account_id bukan UUID"
}
